It is most amazing that the attention of the West was attracted towards Kundalini

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:48.892
through something that is absolutely against Kundalini, which is called as ‘Tantrism’.

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:55.892
I would say Annie Besant, the first who founded this Theosophical Society in India,

00:01:56.000 --> 00:02:04.892
was one of the first ladies who wrote about Kundalini and the Chakras and all that.

