00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:19.892
because Kundalini awakening is a spontaneous happening, It’s spontaneous.

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:32.892
If you can understand a living process of a seed that sprouts by itself.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:41.892
You cannot do it by your intellect, by any effort. It’s a living process.

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:48.892
In the same way, awakening of the Kundalini is a living process.

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:56.892
It’s an evolutionary process, the culminating process, but it is a living process.

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:03.892
And that’s why it cannot be achieved by our thinking, nor through our effort.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:06.892
This is the basis of Sahaja Yoga.

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:11.892
Sahaja – ‘Saha’ means with, ‘Ja’ means born. It is born within you, it is your right.

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:16.892
You are born with it. As we can say, if you buy this from the market,

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:20.892
we know it has a cord with it, to be put to the mains.

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:28.892
In the same way, you have your cord within you, there.

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:32.892
And the whole machinery is built within you.

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:39.892
During your evolutionary process from say from amoeba or say it is from carbon only,

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:45.892
or even earlier, whatever has happened, in creating a human being

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:51.892
has been placed there as milestones in your being.

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:55.892
These are the seven stages through which man has evolved.

00:03:56.000 --> 00:04:02.892
The last stage is only that this Kundalini, this residual force that is settled down there,

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:08.892
has to rise, and is to be connected to the All-pervading Power.

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:16.892
Unless and until this happens, you cannot be convinced about any power

00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:20.892
