You get into the collective consciousness, in which you start feeling others. Now,

00:41:58.000 --> 00:41:59.892
for example, you all have come for the first time,

00:42:00.000 --> 00:42:02.892
but these all know where is your Kundalini now.

00:42:03.000 --> 00:42:04.892
Where are you standing.

00:42:05.000 --> 00:42:08.892
As soon as you get it, you will know. This little boy knows, leave alone [others].

00:42:09.000 --> 00:42:16.892
There’s a little grandchild I have. She’s a born-realised. She knows. She knows.

00:42:17.000 --> 00:42:20.892
If you have that awareness, you know that: this is this and this is this;

00:42:21.000 --> 00:42:24.892
because you can feel it on your fingers, actually subjective.

00:42:25.000 --> 00:42:28.892
It is a subjective knowledge. You can feel it, the heat and everything on your fingers.

00:42:29.000 --> 00:42:31.892
And the fingers have different chakras.

00:42:32.000 --> 00:42:36.892
And you can feel the chakras on your fingers, on your palm,

00:42:37.000 --> 00:42:39.892
and you can see the heat and the cold,

00:42:40.000 --> 00:42:42.892
for which you don’t have to go to any school.

