00:43:07.000 --> 00:43:11.892
Because once this power of parasympathetic – which is autonomous nervous system,

00:43:12.000 --> 00:43:15.892
we cannot control it – starts flowing through your central nervous system

00:43:16.000 --> 00:43:22.892
because of this happening of the central rising of this Kundalini,

00:43:23.000 --> 00:43:26.892
then you start feeling it and you can feel others

00:43:27.000 --> 00:43:31.892
because we are all bound by one single thread,

00:43:32.000 --> 00:43:35.892
which is just to be threaded together.

00:43:36.000 --> 00:43:42.892
And once you are threaded and your attention is on that thread that is within you,

00:43:43.000 --> 00:43:45.892
then you start feeling by moving on that thread,

00:43:46.000 --> 00:43:48.892
which passes through everybody else.

00:43:49.000 --> 00:43:55.892
It’s a very simple thing, like a necklace.

00:43:56.000 --> 00:43:59.892
You are different pearls and there’s one thread passing through.

00:44:00.000 --> 00:44:02.892
Now your attention is outside.

00:44:03.000 --> 00:44:05.892
If I say put your attention inside, you cannot do it.

00:44:06.000 --> 00:44:09.892
But then your attention goes inside. You start feeling your chakras.

00:44:10.000 --> 00:44:12.892
You start seeing yourself. You start seeing within yourself.

00:44:13.000 --> 00:44:16.892
Then there is no need to give you any lecture or anything. You yourself will come and say,

00:44:17.000 --> 00:44:19.892
“Mother, I’m catching on my heart chakra.

00:44:20.000 --> 00:44:24.892
” Means “I am afraid. I have a sense of insecurity.” You’ll just come and say that.

00:44:25.000 --> 00:44:27.892
But you need not say all those things. You just say, “I’m catching on my heart chakra,”

00:44:28.000 --> 00:44:31.892
and it works out. And I’ll tell you how to cure it.

00:44:32.000 --> 00:44:36.892
