00:44:37.000 --> 00:44:40.892
Then he had on the heart because he was doing Hatha Yoga.

00:44:41.000 --> 00:44:46.892
We had all kinds of people here who have got it, who have felt it, and it is there.

00:44:47.000 --> 00:44:54.892
So through reasoning you cannot get it. It has to work out, and it works out.

