00:45:13.000 --> 00:45:16.892
“Why did he raise your hand?” I mean, just imagine!

00:45:17.000 --> 00:45:19.892
The thing is flowing from your hand and you have to raise it

00:45:20.000 --> 00:45:21.892
because unless and until you raise your hand

00:45:22.000 --> 00:45:25.892
you cannot raise the Kundalini of a person, that’s the point.

00:45:26.000 --> 00:45:31.892
But the objection will come, I mean, see the egoistical nature of man.

00:45:32.000 --> 00:45:35.892
If I move my hand like that towards you, immediately the man thinks,

00:45:36.000 --> 00:45:40.892
“Why should she raise her hand like this, what is the, why does she do like this?”

00:45:41.000 --> 00:45:44.892
Now, unless and until you are realised, how am I to tell you?

00:45:45.000 --> 00:45:47.892
When Mohammed Sahib taught people that you must do namaz like this,

00:45:48.000 --> 00:45:51.892
everybody made fun of Him.

00:45:52.000 --> 00:45:54.892
They all said, “What is he talking about?

00:45:55.000 --> 00:45:57.892
How does he say, raise hand like this, do like this, namaz like this?”

00:45:58.000 --> 00:46:01.892
All laughed at him. Not only that, they poisoned him, they tortured his life.

00:46:02.000 --> 00:46:07.892
All such great people have been tortured. But this life you cannot torture Me.

00:46:08.000 --> 00:46:13.892
That is sure. No one can torture Me.

00:46:14.000 --> 00:46:21.892
So this time you are going to get it, whether you like it or not! (Laughter)

00:46:22.000 --> 00:46:27.892
Whether you call Me anything, I am going to do it, and I am going to work it out,

00:46:28.000 --> 00:46:32.892
and it is going to happen. I am determined to do it, and it works out.

00:46:33.000 --> 00:46:36.892
Now, so in the whole, what do you give Me?

00:46:37.000 --> 00:46:40.892
People say, “Mother, it’s very difficult to surrender.”

00:46:41.000 --> 00:46:43.892
I say, “Now what are you surrendering here? I don’t know.”

00:46:44.000 --> 00:46:46.892
What is it you are surrendering?

00:46:47.000 --> 00:46:49.892
I am just saying, surrender to your wisdom.

00:46:50.000 --> 00:46:55.892
Why are you surrendering to Me? What can you give Me? What have you got?

00:46:56.000 --> 00:46:59.892
I mean, this idea of surrendering itself, like Hitler coming

00:47:00.000 --> 00:47:03.892
and shooting you and you surrender at his feet. It’s something like that.

00:47:04.000 --> 00:47:07.892
There is surrendering to yourself.

00:47:08.000 --> 00:47:10.892
It is surrendering to your wisdom.

00:47:11.000 --> 00:47:19.892
What you surrender is your ego and your biased intelligence, which cheats you.

00:47:20.000 --> 00:47:22.892
Rise into your pure intelligence.

00:47:23.000 --> 00:47:27.892
And your superego, which is your conditioning, which is pulling you down,

00:47:28.000 --> 00:47:32.892
dragging you, giving you negativity, doing all kinds of things.

00:47:33.000 --> 00:47:38.892
All that has to be given up, and you have to be free people.

00:47:39.000 --> 00:47:41.892
All your bondages have to be dropped down.

00:47:42.000 --> 00:47:46.892
That’s the main point, is liberation I’m talking about, in the real sense.

00:47:47.000 --> 00:47:51.892
Not the liberation by which all your weaknesses should sit on your head.

00:47:52.000 --> 00:47:59.892
But you should be beyond weaknesses, you should be strong in yourself.

00:48:00.000 --> 00:48:06.892
That is what it is. Then, once you are liberated, you see your efficiency.

00:48:07.000 --> 00:48:12.892
You move like a dynamic personality. It’s a very different thing altogether.

00:48:13.000 --> 00:48:18.892
Unless and until you are liberated from your ego and superego.

00:48:19.000 --> 00:48:21.892
How are you going to function, I can’t understand.

00:48:22.000 --> 00:48:25.892
That’s why the mess is there. Why is the mess in this world?

00:48:26.000 --> 00:48:27.892
Because you are not liberated.

00:48:28.000 --> 00:48:32.892
For that it is necessary that you should be free to choose.

00:48:33.000 --> 00:48:35.892
I cannot entice you to do it.

00:48:36.000 --> 00:48:41.892
At the most I can persuade, I can request you, I can come to your house,

00:48:42.000 --> 00:48:44.892
I’ll be very nice to you. I’ll try my level best because

00:48:45.000 --> 00:48:48.892
I know this is what I should give you because I am a Mother.

00:48:49.000 --> 00:48:55.892
But how can I digest what I give you to eat? That you have to do.

00:48:56.000 --> 00:48:58.892
So let us see how it works out!

00:48:59.000 --> 00:49:00.892
May God bless you.

00:49:01.000 --> 00:49:03.892
How the whole thing works out, maybe.

00:49:04.000 --> 00:49:12.892
It might work out very well and you might all get it in no time.

